headline: Deere earnings, Fed Beige Book, jobless claims: What to Watch
summary: Asking for a Trend host Josh Lipton previews several of the biggest stories to come tomorrow, Wednesday, November 26, including earnings results from Deere & Co (DE) and Li Auto (LI, 2015.HK), the Federal Reserve's Beige Book report, and the latest reading on initial jobless claims. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Asking for a Trend.
